gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 117, Knicks 113
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the Knicks, 117-113. Collin Sexton recorded 26 points, seven assists, and four rebounds for the Jazz, with Lauri Markkanen adding 23 points and eight rebounds in the victory. Julius Randle tallied 32 points and 12 rebounds for the Knicks in the loss. The Jazz improve to 8-16 in the regular season, while the Knicks fall to 13-10.
